---

## 🛠 Recommended Preprocessing Pipeline

1. Verify orientation consistency (RAS format)  
2. Intensity normalization (Z-score per volume)  
3. Optional bias field correction (N4ITK)  
4. Patch extraction for 3D training  
5. Data augmentation (flip, rotation, elastic deformation)  

---

## 📊 Evaluation Metrics

Standard evaluation metrics used in BraTS:

- Dice Similarity Coefficient (DSC)  
- Hausdorff Distance (HD95)  
- Sensitivity  
- Specificity  

